'''Ali Hassan Majrashi''' ({{langx|ar|علي حسن مجرشي}}; born 1 October 1999) is a Saudi Arabian [[football (soccer)|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|right back]] for [[Saudi Pro League]] side [[Al-Ahli Saudi FC|Al-Ahli]] and the [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia national team]].<ref>{{cite web |title=علي مجرشي - Ali Magrashi|url=https://www.kooora.com/?player=138848}}</ref><ref name="soccerway">{{cite web |title=ALI MAJRASHI|url=https://us.soccerway.com/players/ali-majrashi/529505/}}</ref>

==Career==
Majrashi started his career at [[Al Shabab FC (Riyadh)|Al-Shabab]] and is a product of Al-Shabab's youth system. On 30 January 2018, Majrashi made his professional debut for Al-Shabab against [[Al-Ahli Saudi FC|Al-Ahli]] in the Pro League, replacing [[Abdulwahab Jaafer]].<ref>{{cite web |title=AL AHLI VS. AL SHABAB  3 - 2|url=https://us.soccerway.com/matches/2018/01/30/saudi-arabia/pro-league/al-ahli-jeddah/al-shabab-riyadh/2683167/}}</ref> On 11 July 2019, Majrashi signed a five-year professional contract with [[Al-Shabab FC (Riyadh)|Al-Shabab]].<ref>{{cite web |title= مجرشي و الشهراني يتعاقدان مع الشباب السعودي|url=https://www.koraon.com/%D9%83%D9%88%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%A8%D9%8A%D8%A9/%D9%85%D8%AC%D8%B1%D8%B4%D9%8A-%D9%88-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B4%D9%87%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%8A-%D9%8A%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B4%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84/}}</ref> On 30 June 2019, he was chosen in the Saudi scholarship program to develop football talents established by the [[General Sports Authority]].<ref>{{cite web |title= 21 لاعبا يفتتحون برنامج ابتعاث وتطوير المواهب|url=https://arriyadiyah.com/650886}}</ref> On 7 February 2021, Majrashi joined [[Al-Faisaly FC|Al-Faisaly]] on loan.<ref>{{cite web |title=الفيصلي يدمج مجرشي |url=https://arriyadiyah.com/718705}}</ref> He started the [[2021 King Cup Final]] on 27 May 2021 helping Al-Faisaly win their first title.<ref>{{cite web |title=الفيصلي يتوج بكأس الملك لأول مرة في تاريخه |url=https://www.alriyadh.com/1887731}}</ref> On 25 January 2022, Majrashi joined Al-Ahli on a four-year deal.<ref>{{cite web |title=أهلي جدة يتعاقد مع مجرشي لاعب الشباب |url=https://www.alarabiya.net/sport/saudi-sport/2022/01/25/%D8%A3%D9%87%D9%84%D9%8A-%D8%AC%D8%AF%D8%A9-%D9%8A%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%AF-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D9%85%D8%AC%D8%B1%D8%B4%D9%8A-%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B4%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%A8}}</ref>

